709388f-a.title: Manhattan: 6th Avenue - 21st Street (West)
709388f-a.text:
Sixth Avenue, south from W. 21st Street, showing the "E1" demolition gap between this point and its 18th Street station.
February 19, 1939
P. L. Sper
